metadata.name: above the clouds - clarity & trust
metadata.description:
as someone who tends to have my head above the clouds with many creative ideas swirling around my brain, i also would tend to feel overwhelmed & beat myself up for having "so many" ideas that had difficulty manifesting into this reality. throughout my healing journey, i realized that adventuring off to new environments helped bring clarity & trust within myself.

from above the clouds of colorado to start a new weekend adventure in new york, i wish you clarity & trust on your own journey â™¡
